Privacy Policy for Updaty (iOS App)
This privacy policy describes how Updaty collects, uses, and discloses data when you use the app.
Information not collected
Updaty does not collect personal data such as name, email address, location, device information, or other identifiers. We also do not collect any information about your use of the app.
Advertising
Updaty displays advertisements from AdMob, a Google advertising network. AdMob may collect and use data about your device activity to display personalized ads. For more information on AdMob's privacy practices, please refer to Google's privacy policy.
Linked websites
This app loads images from our server [Server-URL] to support app functionality. We adhere to our privacy policy and do not collect any personal data through image transmission.
IP address in server logs
When you access our website, we may store your IP address in our server logs to troubleshoot technical issues and ensure the security of our website. This information is automatically deleted after seven days and is not used for any other purposes.
Changes to this privacy policy
We reserve the right to change this privacy policy at any time. Changes will be posted on this page. Please check this page regularly for updates.
Contact us
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us
